Returns: the string representation of this origin
getOrigin().Description: Gets the string representation of this origin.

Returns: the total amount of storage, in bytes
getUsage().Description: Gets the total amount of storage currently being used by this origin, for all JavaScript storage APIs, in bytes.

getQuota().Description: Gets the quota for this origin, for the Web SQL Database API, in bytes. If this origin does not use the Web SQL Database API, this quota will be set to zero.

ClassDesc: This class encapsulates information about the amount of storage currently used by an origin for the JavaScript storage APIs. An origin comprises the host, scheme and port of a URI. See @B_android#webkit#WebStorage_E@ for details.
